#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-ons manager
#: buildVars.py:26
msgid ""
"A white‑noise and ambient‑sound plugin for NVDA with multi‑track playback "
"and full support for user‑supplied audio."
msgstr ""
"伶伦是一款为 NVDA 设计的白噪声与环境音播放插件，支持多音轨播放、独立音量控"
"制、随机播放等功能，并提供简单易用的设置界面。"
